# Folder Structure Rules

## Decision Tree вЂ” Run This Before Placing Any File

```
Is it used on 2+ UNRELATED pages?
  вњ… YES в†’ src/components/ui/
  вќЊ NO  в†’
    Is it a layout shell (Navbar, Footer, TopBar)?
      вњ… YES в†’ src/components/common/[Name]/
      вќЊ NO  в†’
        Is it shared across 2+ pages in the SAME section?
          вњ… YES в†’ src/pages/[SectionGroup]/components/
          вќЊ NO  в†’ src/pages/[PageName]/components/
```

